name: Api
desc: Handles all the api calls

name: createComment
desc: Sends a Comment creation request to the Api

name: createPost
desc: Sends a Post creation request to the Api

name: createUser
desc: Sends a User creation request to the Api

name: getAllBoards
desc: Returns a list of every Board

name: getAllPostsByDate
desc: Returns a list of every Post by date ascendant

name: getPostsFromBoard
desc: Returns a list of every Post of a specified Board

name: logIn
desc: Sends a Log In request to the Api

name: Board
desc: Model of a Board

name: createState
desc: Creates the mutable state for this widget at a given location in the tree.

name: TotoController
desc: The main controller of the application

name: buildAccessButton
desc: Returns a button for both accesses and calls TotoController.signUp or TotoController.logIn

name: buildBoardFeed
desc: Calls controller/Api.getPostsFromBoard On a successful response builds every post of the asked Board. While loading it shows a CircularProgressIndicator. On a failure response it displays an Icon that onTap tries again.

name: buildComment
desc: Renders the Comment widget with the submitted data

name: buildCommentMedia
desc: Builds the Media for a Comment, calls for TotoController.isFileVideo to call either TotoController.buildMediaVideo or TotoController.buildMediaImage

name: buildGeneralFeed
desc: Calls controller/Api.getAllPostsByDate On a successful response builds every post of the server chronologically ascendant. While loading it shows a CircularProgressIndicator. On a failure response it displays an Icon that onTap tries again.

name: buildMainPost
desc: Renders the Post widget with the submitted data on the PostViewPage

name: buildMedia
desc: Builds the Media for a Post, calls for TotoController.isFileVideo to call either TotoController.buildMediaVideo or TotoController.buildMediaImage

name: buildMediaImage
desc: Renders the image given the filename, retrieving it from the server

name: buildMediaVideo
desc: Renders the video given the filename, retrieving it from the server

name: buildPost
desc: Renders the Post widget with the submitted data

name: buildPostComments
desc: Builds the comments of a Post, calling TotoController.buildMainPost and consequently their comments with Toto.buildComment

name: checkEmail
desc: Whether the email given is coherent

name: checkFileType
desc: Whether the media type of the file is in the accepted types list

name: countComments
desc: Returns an icon with the number of comments of that Post

name: getBoardHeader
desc: Returns the header of a Board Page given its destination and widget

name: getHeader
desc: Returns the header given its destination and widget

name: hasMediaComment
desc: Whether the comment has media

name: hasMediaPost
desc: Whether the Post has media

name: isFileVideo
desc: Whether the file type is a video

name: logIn
desc: Checks if the parameters are correct

name: loggedIn
desc: Writes in the device the username and sets true the loggedIn bool

name: loggedOut
desc:
Erases the data stored in the device and resets the variables of username
and loggedIn

name: setComment
desc: Calls Api.createComment and returns a Snack bar with the response.

name: signUp
desc: Checks if the parameters are correct

name: listTile
desc: Builds the elements of the drawer

name: logOut
desc: Builds the logout element

name: regularDrawer
desc: Builds the Drawer of the app

desc: Creates the mutable state for this widget at a given location in the tree.

name: build
desc: Describes the part of the user interface represented by this widget.

name: main
desc: Runs the application and checks if there is preferences stored in the device.
